 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Compound</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/\">PubChem</a> - One of the biggest chemical database such as compounds, genes and proteins.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ebi.ac.uk/chebi/\">ChEBI</a> - Chemical database  focused on small chemical compounds.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ebi.ac.uk/chembl/\">ChEMBL</a> - Database of bioactive molecules with drug-like properties.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.chemspider.com/\">ChemSpider</a> - Chemical structure database.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.genome.jp/kegg/compound/\">KEGG COMPOUND</a> - Collection of small molecules and biopolymers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.lipidmaps.org/databases/lmsd/overview\">LIPID MAPS</a> - Database of lipids.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"pathway\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pathway\" aria-label=\"pathway permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Pathway</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.pathwaycommons.org/\">PathwayCommon</a> - Database of Pathways and Interactions.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.genome.jp/kegg/pathway.html\">KEGG PATHWAY</a> - Collection fo drawn pathway maps.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wikipathways.org/\">WikiPathways</a> - Database of biological pathways.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"mass-spectra\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mass-spectra\" aria-label=\"mass spectra permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Mass Spectra</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.massbank.jp/\">MassBank</a> - Open souce databases and tools for mass spectrometry reference spectra.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mona.fiehnlab.ucdavis.edu/\">MoNA MassBank of North America</a> - Meta database of metabolite mass spectra, metadata and associated compounds.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"protein\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#protein\" aria-label=\"protein permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Protein</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.proteinatlas.org/\">THE HUMAN PROTEIN ATLAS</a> - One of the biggest human protein database contained cells, tissues, and organs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.rcsb.org/\">PROTEIN DATA BANK</a> - Database of the 3D shapes of proteins, nucleic acids, and complex assemblies.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.uniprot.org/\">UniProt</a> - The collection of functional information on proteins.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"genome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#genome\" aria-label=\"genome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Genome</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/projects/genome/guide/human/index.shtml\">Human Genome Resources at NCBI</a> - Database of image, proteomics, transcriptomics and systems biology.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genbank/\">GenBank</a> - Database of genetic sequence offered by NCBI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://genome.ucsc.edu/\">UCSC Genome Browser</a> - Genome blowser offered by UCSC.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"disease\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#disease\" aria-label=\"disease permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Disease</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.genome.jp/kegg/drug/\">KEGG DRUG</a> - Comprehensive drug information resource for approved drugs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.drugbank.com/\">DrugBank</a> - A database of drug and target maintained by the University of Alberta.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"interaction\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#interaction\" aria-label=\"interaction permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Interaction</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Drug Gene Interaction\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.dgidb.org/\">DGIdb</a> - A database of drug-gene interactions and the druggable genome.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://ctdbase.org/\">Comparative Toxicogenomics Database</a> - A database of Chemical-gene interactions, Chemical-disease associations, Gene-disease associations, and Chemical-phenotype associations.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Chemical Protein Interaction\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://stitch.embl.de/\">STITCH</a> - A database of Chemical Protein Interaction.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"preprocess\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#preprocess\" aria-label=\"preprocess permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Preprocess</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/cdk/cdk\">Chemistry Development Kit</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.